2008-11-26 18:16 UTC+0100 Miguel Angel Marchuet <miguelangel@marchuet.net>
   * common.mak
   * compile.mak
   + source\common\hbwince.c
     + Added file with wc (WIDECHAR) functions

   * include\hbapigt.h
   * include\hbgtcore.h
   * source\rtl\gtapi.c
